Dear Haechan, 

I know this message might mean nothing here. This is just my heartfelt confession as a sunflower.

I don't know what this company's problem is with you. You should try to demand more from your company as you are rightful so. 

It's been years since you debuted and not much solo activity under your name? As a sunflower, I appreciate your hard work but it's time to spend your energy and motivation for things other than your group. 

If you plan to renew with SM, do consider renewing your terms.

We hope that you know your worth and talent is better than what SM has been telling you.
